## Limitations

This report is limited by the availability of sources and the inherent bias in self-reported opinions on platforms like forums and personal blogs. Additionally, the complexity of the abortion debate means that not all perspectives can be fully captured in a single report. The focus was primarily on the reasons for opposition, which may not encompass the full spectrum of the debate, including pro-choice arguments and the nuances within each stance.